n4PdwA">Sơ đông phụng chỉ tứ dực vận công thần - 初冬奉旨賜翊運功臣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u-t%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-08/poem-ybCQBh0AFD5cfxUSJmxf8Q">Tần Châu tạp thi kỳ 08 - 秦州雜詩其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%C6%B0-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-c%E1%BA%A3m-th%E1%BB%8B/poem-84wUxhYuHz8lkRl2LJ95ew">Thư đường cảm thị - 書堂感示</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-tam-t%E1%BB%AD-Thi%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A1/poem-0xk1QF8_Aqf5qUjE6ECGKA">Thương đệ tam tử Thiên Hoá - 傷第三子天化</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
